OL,7,FA woman who survived alcohol poisoning
OL,8,Fin Laos which killed six backpackers,
OL,9,Fincluding her friend, said travellers
OL,10,Fheading abroad this Summer should be
OL,11,Faware of the dangers as she campaigned
OL,12,Fto get issue added to the school
OL,13,Fcurriculum.
OL,15,FBethany Clarke was taken to hospital
OL,16,Fafter allegedly being served drinks
OL,17,Flaced with methanol in the popular
OL,18,Fbackpacking town of Vang Vieng last
OL,19,Fyear.
