OL,7,FHer best friend Simone White, 28, from
OL,8,FOrpington died and the government in
OL,9,FLaos said it was "profoundly saddened".
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News London Bethany
OL,12,Fcalled on the government to do more to
OL,13,Feducate teenagers in schools about the
OL,14,Fdangers of drinking alcohol abroad.
OL,16,F"For me it's what happens when I'm
OL,17,Fdead - is this message going to still
OL,18,Fbe delivered in 100 years time?"
OL,19,FBethany told ITV News London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
