OL,7,F"History has this thing of repeating
OL,8,Fitself so I guess the idea of all of
OL,9,Fthis is to try and make sure it's in
OL,10,Fthe curriculum so that no one has to
OL,11,Fgo through this again in the future,"
OL,12,Fshe explained.
OL,14,FBethany started an online campaign
OL,15,Fhoping to force a debate in the
OL,16,FCommons on whether the dangers of
OL,17,Fmethanol poisoning should be put on
OL,18,Fthe school curriculum.
