OL,7,F"We're just going to keep going - the
OL,8,Fpetition will expire in October so
OL,9,Fwe're just going to keep pushing,
OL,10,Ftrying to get the message out as much
OL,11,Fas we can," she added.
OL,13,FThe government has added methanol
OL,14,Fpoisoning to the list of risks in some
OL,15,Fcountries on its travel advice website.
OL,17,FIn Laos it says Tiger Vodka and Tiger
OL,18,FWhiskey - the spirits the hostel is
OL,19,Fbelieved to have served that night -
OL,20,Fare now banned.
