OL,7,FThe Foreign Office advice on its
OL,8,FTravel Aware Instagram page is to
OL,9,F"stick to sealed drinks".
OL,11,FBut Bethany wants a stronger message
OL,12,Fdelivered to children at a younger age.
OL,14,FShe said: "Maybe some kind of
OL,15,Freenactment with a film would be quite
OL,16,Fuseful.
OL,18,F"Those videos you used to get in
OL,19,Fschool of watching the car crashes and
OL,20,Fthings like that.
