OL,7,F"I remember them being quite scary at
OL,8,Fthe time and they come back to you
OL,9,Fmany years later - so it just sticks
OL,10,Fin your head.
OL,12,F"And I think that's what we need
OL,13,Fsometimes, something similar to that."
OL,15,FThe hostel owner has previously denied
OL,16,Fshots given at their bar were
OL,17,Fresponsible for the poisoning.
