OL,7,FBethany said they ordered five or six
OL,8,Fshots each over the course of two-and-
OL,9,Fa-half hours and said the drinks did
OL,10,Fnot taste as strong as she expected,
OL,11,Fthen they started to feel unwell the
OL,12,Fnext day.
OL,14,FShe described feeling tired and "just
OL,15,Fnot really being able to move the
OL,16,Fmuscles that you want to move when you
OL,17,Fwant to move them".
OL,19,FWhen Simone started being sick, and
OL,20,FBethany fainted, their friend
OL,21,Fsuggested they go to hospital.
